textBox.richText: Alli had rugby in vegas this weekend...Gunter came out, and we carried on the “boy’s weekend” tradition. He got some Icelandic Keepers...took ‘em in on Saturday to get ‘em mounted, and picked them up on Sunday. Saturday was spent making laps in the upper switchyard trees.
